reviewText: I thought this video was amateur, did not include a single symbol, was based on opinions of reiki practioners who are unknowns...for all we know they are relatives of the videoographers...

This video is a clean and clear ABC explanation of Reiki energy and it's applications.  Be advised, however, that it does not describe, discuss or mention actual Reiki Healing Symbols, so the title will be misleading to  Reiki practitioners.
